import React from 'react';
import {BrowserRouter, NavLink, Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom';

import LogoSentry from './assets/logo-sentry.svg'

import Issues from './pages/issues'
import Services from './pages/services'
import Explore from './pages/explore'
import Dashboards from './pages/dashboards'

import Page from './layouts/page'
import Navigation from './layouts/navigation'
import NavItem from './layouts/navitem'

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Page>
        <Navigation>
          <NavItem><LogoSentry/></NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to='/'>IS</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to='/services/frontend'>SE</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to='/explore/spans'>EX</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to='/dashboards/all'>DA</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
        </Navigation>
        <Routes>
          <Route path='/' element={<Issues/>}/>
          <Route path='/issues/saved1' element={<Issues/>}/>
          <Route path='/issues/saved2' element={<Issues/>}/>

          <Route path='/services/frontend' element={<Services/>}/>
          <Route path='/services/backend' element={<Services/>}/>
          <Route path='/services/mobile' element={<Services/>}/>

          <Route path='/explore/spans' element={<Explore/>}/>
          <Route path='/explore/errors' element={<Explore/>}/>
          <Route path='/explore/replays' element={<Explore/>}/>          
          <Route path='/explore/logs' element={<Explore/>}/>

          <Route path='/dashboards/all' element={<Dashboards/>}/>
          <Route path='/dashboards/saved1' element={<Dashboards/>}/>
          <Route path='/dashboards/saved2' element={<Dashboards/>}/>
        </Routes>
      </Page>
    </BrowserRouter>
  );
}

export default App;
